    "It is particularly valuable when understanding an image semantically, like identifying objects and interactions in a scene.",
    "Image2Text[image], which generates captions for the image and detects words in the image.",
    "You are recommended to use it first to get more information about the image to the question.",
    "If the question contains an image, it will return the caption and OCR text, else, it will return None.",
    "For example, Image2Text[image]."
